Multi-Vendor Marketplace

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509822943338{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Launch Your Own Etsy Style Marketplace With Rigid Theme. Allow vendors to create individual stores, manage their inventories and shipping while you can earn commission on their sales.
[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1495396679742{margin-bottom: 10px !important;}"]Powered by:[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="4905" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822228279{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css_animation="appear" css=".vc_custom_1502934725489{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}"]

Compatible With Both Free and PRO Versions of:

[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="4905" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822263812{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_single_image image="4907" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822294108{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509822971289{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"]*WC Marketplace and WC Vendors are FREE third-party plugins fully integrated with custom Rigid theme styles and features.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation="appear" css=".vc_custom_1495471113377{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Marketplace Features

[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495471363813{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Single store multiple sellers

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509822980687{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Allow multiple sellers / vendors to customize, clone and sell products and make your marketplace lucrative for buyers. While admin will have more WC vendors in the marketplace with products, buyers will have galore of options to compare and shop.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="4911" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822391596{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4915" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822408269{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495471776053{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Marketplace Sellers Dashboard

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509822989542{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
A user-friendly dashboard for marketplace vendors offering a snapshot of their most important tasks. The feature-rich dashboard guides them to manage their products, commission, track orders and plenty more. All that from one place.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495471907799{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Admin Notifications to Vendors

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823000877{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Share important information with your Sellers or guide them to set up their stores- WC Marketplace allows site admin to communicate with all vendors via a universal message board.
Admin can also shoot off quick announcement to notify changes, updates of the marketplace.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="4910" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822425264{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4913" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822442840{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495472113293{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Commission Disbursal Management

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823012051{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
In WC Marketplace, admin can automatically disburse commission to vendors hourly, daily, monthly and fortnightly. Or, the vendors can manually request to the admin for commission disbursal. Plus, both the admin and vendor can track all their previous transactions.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495472286986{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Vendors Review Management

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823031197{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Buyers at your marketplace can rate and review a vendor. Admin controls the review system and can optionally enable only those buyers to rate who have purchased from respective vendors.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="4916" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822462976{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4909" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822485258{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495472463966{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Vendor Capabilities Management

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823040422{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
From uploading product data, accessing export data to send a message to the buyer or make changes in policy settings - help your WC vendors to customize their stores and make it flexible for a hassle free operation.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495472630760{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Admin Taskbar

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823049277{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Notification board for the site admin to quickly finish tasks. Reject or approve vendor, transfer WC vendor commission and or just keep a tab on the marketplace- managing a multi vendor store is now a breeze for you.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="4912" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822495371{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4917" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822597910{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495472795785{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Multiple Payment Channels

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823060815{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Admin can disburse Multi vendor commission through payment gateways (PayPal & Stripe) or go for Direct bank Transfer. Admin has the option to settle for the payment through fixed amount, percentage amount or a combination of both.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495473011828{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Coupon Management

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1509823074460{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"]
Admin can set global coupon or allow vendors to issue a coupon for all products in one click or let them manually select each of their preferred product.
Give more options to your WC vendors and let them fix their promotional strategy by issuing coupon with the discount on the entire cart or product/s, in absolute values or in percentage.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_single_image image="4914" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822622806{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1495471635512{border-bottom-width: 1px !important;padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;border-bottom-color: #f1f1f1 !important;border-bottom-style: dashed !important;}"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="4908" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1509822636254{margin-bottom: 60px !important;}"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1495396321043{padding-right: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;}"][vc_column_text css_animation="none" css=".vc_custom_1495473126647{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"]

Multiple Commission types
